Three people died and several people were injured in an accident near the Sasol Garage on the N11 (Groblersdal road) at approximately 16:20 today. The driver of the SUV, as well as two other passengers were seriously injured. Three more passengers were slightly injured. The three people who died on the scene, were also passengers in the vehicle. There were 12 people in the SUV, which is an indication that it was overloaded.    